え Initial loop state.
え Sum starts at 0.
え Current number starts at 1.
え The modulo-3 and modulo-5 states both start at remainder 1.
上げる ハジメ は 「「「「クミ」足す「JフッJエッエ」」足す「JフッJエッ「フ」足す「エ」」」足す「サイチ」」足す「ゴイチ」


え Run the loop and return the accumulated sum.
え センマエ is 999, so ステプ is applied once for each number 1..999.
え Finally, イチ extracts field 1 from the resulting state tuple: the sum.
